Java Highlight grid Program.
The impact of it is that it forms a square grid of size (N) by (N) with random even numbers among 2 and 20 and formats as well as displays such a grid in a form of a grid and the user has to decide what number to underline in such a grid. The program has succeeded therein to highlight all the incidences of the same figure as well as the occurrence rate of the instances.

Features
Generate a grid of NxN numerical grid.

Mark even numbers (2 -20) on the grid randomly.

Sketches the grid in an organised manner.

Enters a number that is highlighted by the user and the number is between 2 and 20.

Whatever leads to events with [X].

Cumulative Counts and Refers The number of times it has happened.

Invalid data transaction and non-numeric data transaction.

Executed at the command line.
